{
  "stem": "26728.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right, the main-- that was where the airbase was that we were-- that we were stationed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was also part of the Seventh Army headquarters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and keep in mind, this would be like Los Angeles International Airport is today.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was just airplanes coming out your ears.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Just-- it was really a dangerous place to fly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what they did was they split the squadrons up from the various groups and moved the little airplanes to satellite strips, which is what they call them-- satellite strips-- and what it would be would be a big field someplace, where they would put down the steel matting if it was necessary.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we would be-- the 16 airplanes, the pilots, and the crews would be-- that would be their base, all within 20, 30, 40 miles of Frankfort, 60 tops.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One of the plays-- and this is where I met a German family that became close, and I've seen them a couple of times since the war.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We continued to fly the targets of opportunity missions, air to ground support through March.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and it's kind of ironic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't get to be-- I was trained as a fighter pilot, and I was-- and I got in several dogfights, as we called them, with other-- with German airplanes.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I got-- well, I'm credited with a kill and a half, which means I got one, and I shared a kill with another one, with another pilot.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So in the Air Force they give you credit for a half.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If you both got the guy, and they don't know who got him for sure, they give you each half.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Navy doesn't do that.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
